{"tid":2015628,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"和你SING X 和你SHOP 二合一 威力加強版","createTime":"2020-05-13T22:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T12:37:29.000Z","uid":8170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8f42df72af8e9016efbef4a695cfffc6b8aeef","tid":2015628,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T22:55:30.000Z","msg":"「和你SING」主線係要唱歌集氣，副線係要<span style=\"color: gold;\">「班狗入商場封舖趕人」</span>，製造<span style=\"color: gold;\">「班狗攪死經濟」</span>嘅現象。<br />\n<br />\n但一路就咁 loop 住<span style=\"color: gold;\">「聚人」、「等狗嚟」、「狗趕人走」、「商場關門」</span>，好快商舖就會有反感，班狗就越來越冇顧忌。<br />\n<br />\n但如果加埋「和你SHOP」元素落去就唔同玩法了，首先入商場唔係企唔係唱，係去幫襯下啲舖頭（最好係黃店啦），過一陣先出返去唱，引狗入場掃場，就可以造返一個「<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實和你SING係帶旺人流同商店收入」</span>嘅勢出嚟，加強<span style=\"color: gold;\">「狗嚟就冇生意做」</span>嘅形象。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">當然，狗嚟，又過晒最旺時間，就應該走喇。</span>"},{"pid":"5856ceeb303dd2af8a4dceb8e9c893d123ec4a4e","tid":2015628,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:02:57.000Z","msg":"幫襯商入邊既黃店"},{"pid":"a3dc7a399f0e851711f3dbd303d802dd1b2b31d2","tid":2015628,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:04:04.000Z","msg":"好少見商場入面有黃店&hellip;"},{"pid":"1535c440413c2cec2d2ff1e3d77d1907378071bb","tid":2015628,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3dc7a399f0e851711f3dbd303d802dd1b2b31d2","tid":2015628,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:04:04.000Z","msg":"好少見商場入面有黃店&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:53:28.000Z","msg":"推 唔到 但有得諗"},{"pid":"c0886804d8e663a74ae8c3c334547dbe9345d376","tid":2015628,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"自推一下。"}]}